v_products_description_1: Freshly breaded, flash fried and made to order every time. Served with a chili aioli.
Something great just got better! We take our hand-tossed dough, melt a generous amount of cheese and add garlic butter. Served with marinara.
Our tender breast of chicken, coated in blackening spice, folded in our own pizza dough with cheddar, mozzarella, cool ranch, peppers and onions.
Fresh roma tomatoes tossed in balsamic vinegar and olive oil, accompanied by crispy parmesan toast points, covered in pesto-marinated fresh mozzarella.
We hand-batter our local curds the day they are made. This is a Wisconsin tradition and the best you have had! Served with ranch dipping sauce.
Artichoke hearts blended with a four-cheese blend and a touch of spice. Served with fresh-baked focaccia points.

We've combined the signature flavors of our Spicy Garlic Pasta recipe and set them on a light and crispy flatbread. Only the freshest of ingredients ? grilled chicken, shredded mozzarella, parmesan, mushrooms, saut?ed garlic and basil. We finish the dish with olive oil, chili sauce and a pinch of parsley.

A refreshing combination of grilled chicken, shredded mozzarella, caramelized onions, tangy barbecue sauce and cilantro creates the foundation for a pizza that will surely leave you wanting more. Crisp and light, yet robust in flavor.

Get daring and set your taste buds on fire.  A light and crispy flatbread topped w/ grilled chicken marinated in buffalo sauce, freshly sliced red onion, bleu cheese crumbles and mozzarella.  Ranch dressing completes this unique and dynamic combination of flavors.

A new twist on an old favorite. We start with grilled chicken, ranch dressing, mozzarella cheese, cheddar cheese, bacon, shredded lettuce and roma tomatoes then  finish with a drizzle of ranch dressing.
Choose one-half of any one of our delicious panini sandwiches and couple it with either our homemade Chicken and Wild Rice Soup or the Soup of the Day selection.
Our Caesar salad is made from our own Caesar dressing tossed with croutons, fresh parmesan cheese and romaine lettuce.
Pears tossed with a warm honey balsamic vinaigrette, baby greens, spinach, bleu cheese, pistachio nuts and dried cranberries.
Fresh spinach with spiced pecans, bleu cheese and dried cranberries tossed in a tarragon vinaigrette.
Fresh baby spinach tossed in mango vinaigrette, topped with pineapple, craisins, spiced pecans, parmesan and our from-scratch jerk glazed chicken breast.
Fresh baby spinach and roma tomatoes tossed in balsamic vinegar and olive oil, accompanied by fresh pesto-marinated mozzarella and pesto-grilled chicken with crispy toast points.
Fresh romaine tossed with tomatoes, kalamata olives, cucumbers, onions, feta cheese and a special Greek dressing.
Fresh romaine lettuce tossed in our own Caesar dressing with croutons, chicken and fresh parmesan cheese in our tortilla wrap.
Fresh romaine lettuce, spiced pecans, grilled blackened chicken breast, bleu cheese dressing, chopped tomatoes, cheese and red onions in our honey and beer pizza dough.
Grilled chicken with peppers, lettuce, onions, cheese and southwest seasonings wrapped in our fresh honey and beer pizza dough.
Pesto-grilled chicken breast, sun-dried tomato olive tapenade, tomatoes, roasted red peppers and fresh spinach tossed with Greek dressing and mozzarella cheese on honey and beer pizza dough.
We take our pizza dough, cover it in cheddar cheese then fill it up with bacon, ranch dressing, lettuce, tomato and a grilled chicken breast.

Let the excitement begin with a fresh flour tortilla stuffed with spicy buffalo chicken tenders, crisp lettuce, sun-ripened roma tomatoes and shredded cheddar cheese then topped off with our own buttermilk ranch dressing.

Pesto-grilled chicken breast with fresh tomatoes marinated in balsamic vinegar and spices, provolone cheese, crushed pesto croutons and a Greek feta cheese dressing. All rolled in a spinach tortilla wrap.
Ranch dressing, Canadian bacon, Swiss cheese, lightly breaded chicken breast, lettuce and tomatoes all stacked inside a lightly grilled sourdough bread.
Lightly grilled sourdough bread filled with smoked turkey, smoked ham, cheddar cheese, tomatoes, bacon, mayo, lettuce and barbecue sauce.
Pesto-grilled chicken breast, sun-dried tomato olive tapenade, tomatoes, roasted red peppers and fresh spinach tossed with Greek dressing and provolone cheese on lightly grilled sourdough.
Lightly grilled sourdough bread filled with smoked turkey, artichoke spread, tomatoes, lettuce and provolone cheese.

Juicy Italian beef covered in pickled giardiniera (a quickly pickled, spicy Italian salad of mixed vegetables) served on a fresh-toasted French roll. Finished with shredded mozzarella and paired with a side of au jus.
A juicy half-pound burger char-broiled to your liking. Served on a Telera roll with leaf lettuce, tomatoes and a dill pickle spear.
Char-grilled half-pound burger basted with our own whiskey barbecue sauce and topped with cheddar cheese.
Made with rum and espresso soaked ladyfingers, mascarpone cheese and an Italian egg custard then topped with chocolate cocoa. This is sure to warm your belly.
The most basic of French desserts?vanilla custard encrusted with caramelized sugar.
Awesome creamy caramel cheesecake baked on a sweet and salty almond crust topped with a thick bed of buttery caramel and a sprinkle of more almonds. Made with gluten-free ingredients.
Chocolate mousse layered between chocolate decadence cake, finished off with chocolate ganache. Served with whipped cream.
Freshly sliced apple filling with our unique sweet dumplings, baked to perfection, with caramel glaze drizzled over all.
An Italian favorite! Made with fresh cream, parmesan cheese and a touch of fresh garlic tossed with fettuccine.
Garlic and Italian spices sauteed in a tomato meat sauce, tossed with spaghetti and topped with parmesan.
Lightly breaded chicken breast, pan-fried then baked in the oven, served over marinara fettuccine then topped off with our special cheese blend and fresh parsley.
A fresh tomato sauce tossed with artichokes, kalamata olives, onions, grilled mushrooms, sun-dried tomatoes and feta cheese over linguine.
Twin sheets of pasta stuffed with grilled chicken breast, ricotta and parmesan cheeses, spinach and red onions, then baked in a rich pistachio cream sauce and topped with our special cheese blend.

Start with sauteed chicken, mixed peppers and roasted red pepper puree. Then add a hint of garlic and cooked in a gourmet cream sauce, tossed together with a red pepper fettuccine and a pinch of parmesan.
Marsala wine, sauteed chicken, fresh portobello mushroom caps, sauteed to perfection. Then tossed with fettuccine, parmesan cream sauce and topped with fresh-shredded parmesan.
This dish starts with two pasta sheets stuffed with bay scallops, crab meat and shrimp. We top it off with cheese and bake it to perfection in our seafood & sherry wine sauce.
Fettuccine tossed with chicken, white wine, fresh basil and garlic in a sun-dried tomato pesto parmesan cream sauce.
Spicy peanut ginger sauce tossed with chicken, garlic, carrots, green onions, bean sprouts and rigatoni pasta.

Our sauce is made from a shot of tequila, lime juice and a spicy cream sauce. Filled with sweet red, yellow and green peppers, onions, cilantro and tequila-glazed chicken and tossed with red pepper fettuccine. This is a house favorite!
Classic Italian sausage with grilled mushrooms in a tomato cream sauce tossed over fettuccine and garnished with oregano.
Shrimp and scallops sauteed with garlic, onions, grilled mushrooms, sweet peppers and fresh basil in a lemon wine marinara tossed together with linguini. You may also try this with our alfredo sauce.
Rigatoni tossed with chicken, fresh basil, grilled mushrooms, red chilies, parmesan cheese and lots of garlic.
Our old family recipe of homemade macaroni and cheese ? a childhood favorite.
This is a classic Italian lasagna with our own unique flair of red wine, cumin, fresh oregano, mozzarella cheese, ricotta cheese, garlic and our own blend of Italian sausage and seasonings.
A perfect blend of ricotta, parmesan, red onion and spinach between two layers of pasta, served with your choice of a savory meat sauce or marinara. A Grazies classic.
Sauteed chicken and mushrooms in a spicy vodka-tomato cream sauce with a touch of garlic. Tossed with rigatoni and parmesan.

Treat your taste buds to rich and decadent delight. This fresh-from-scratch favorite will warm your heart and palate. It includes an intricate blend of hearty gnocchi, saut?ed garlic, red onion, Wisconsin cheddar cheese, sour cream, bacon, grilled chicken and a pinch of chives.
Sauteed chicken, white wine, fresh garlic, salt and pepper. Made with fresh basil pesto, tossed with gourmet cream, grilled button mushrooms and fresh-grated parmesan cheese.

We welcome a new addition to our pasta family. This spicy new creation starts with garlic, grilled mushrooms, fresh red onions, sauteed chicken, pistachios and a spicy chili pistachio cr?me that is tossed together with linguini.

A mildly spicy dish starting with noodles covered with a perfect balance of marinara, fresh mozzarella cheese, crushed red pepper, Italian sausage and finished with more melted fresh mozzarella cheese.

This pasta starts with a light sauce, fresh cream and a spiced style curry. We add sweet mixed peppers, mushrooms, green onions, broccoli and saut?ed chicken to make a very flavorful sauce tossed over angel hair.
This steak is season-rubbed then char-grilled to perfection. Exceptionally juicy and flavorful.
This steak is marinated and season-rubbed then char-grilled and accompanied with caramelized onions. Exceptionally tender and flavorful! Center cut.
We char-grill our fresh 12 oz. Black Angus Ribeye and then add our own sweet and spicy Jack Daniels Whiskey glaze. Grilled to perfection.
Grilled with our own sweet and spicy Jack Daniels Whiskey glaze. A great twist on an old favorite.
Put another log on the fire and enjoy our lightly breaded and delectably seasoned walleye, pan-fried to perfection.
A Grazies classic! We take our pan-fried cabin walleye and add an amaretto and almond reduction.
Ahi Tuna caught in the wild, steak-seared medium rare with blackening spices and caramelized soy, served atop a bed of bleu cheese walnut risotto. No potato choice.

We take our from-scratch honey and beer pizza dough, stuff it with cheese, Canadian bacon, sausage, pepperoni and bacon, roll it all up, bake it and bring it out ready for you to enjoy! Served with a side of fresh pizza sauce.

Slow-cooked to fall off the bone tenderness. Slathered with your choice of sauce: spicy Texas BBQ sauce or honey BBQ sauce. Served with your choice of two sides.

Cedar-seasoned grilled chicken on cranberry pecan rice and quinoa with granny smith apple relish and lemon vinaigrette.
Grilled chicken breast and stir-fried veggies are tossed in a sweet and spicy sauce, served on a bed of rice and topped with crispy wonton strips and sliced green onions.

An Italian classic with crispy chicken covered in warm marinara sauce topped with melted mozzarella and parmesan cheeses. Served on a bed of fettuccine pasta and sprinkled with fresh parsley. Served with a golden brown signature breadstick brushed with garlic and parsley butter.
Juicy chicken breast seasoned and grilled over an open flame. Served with your choice of two sides.

v_products_description_1: 6 oz. Cedar-seasoned grilled salmon with a maple mustard glaze. Served with your choice of two sides.
Golden, crispy-battered fish fillet with fries. Comes with our signature coleslaw, tartar sauce and a lemon wedge.
Stir-fried shrimp and veggies are tossed in a sweet and spicy sauce, served on a bed of rice and topped with crispy wonton strips and sliced green onions.
Crispy battered shrimp are fried golden brown. Served with cocktail sauce, tartar sauce, our signature coleslaw and fries.

Asiago, parmesan and white cheddar cheeses are mixed with penne pasta in a rich parmesan cream sauce then topped with grilled chicken breast and bruschetta tomatoes. Served with a golden brown signature breadstick brushed with garlic and parsley butter.

v_products_description_1: A sweet and savory take on comfort food, four-cheese mac & cheese is topped with crispy breaded chicken tenders tossed in honey pepper sauce and topped with applewood-smoked bacon. Served with a golden brown signature breadstick brushed with garlic and parsley butter.

Juicy grilled chicken or blackened shrimp, served warm on a bed of fettuccine pasta tossed with broccoli and rich Alfredo sauce topped with parmesan cheese. Served with a golden brown signature breadstick brushed with garlic and parsley butter.

v_products_name_1: Creamy Penne Pasta w/ Sliced Prime Rib
v_products_description_1: Penne pasta and tender, thinly sliced prime rib tossed in a hearty, Parmesan cream mushroom sauce with sundried tomato. Finished with Parmesan cheese and a sprinkle of parsley.

v_products_name_1: Chef Bulgarelli's Stuffed Rigatoni & Tomato Meat Sauce
v_products_description_1: Ricotta and Romano cheese-stuffed rigatoni tossed in a savory tomato-basil ground beef sauce with bruschetta tomatoes. Topped with Mozzarella and Parmesan cheeses, then baked until light golden brown. Served with a sprinkle of parsley.

Tart, fresh and flavorful mixed greens are tossed in a sweet lemon olive oil vinaigrette with garden tomatoes and red onions. Topped with grilled chicken, sliced almonds, fresh strawberries and a drizzle of balsamic glaze.
A long-running favorite, crispy breaded or grilled chicken tenders top a bed of Asian greens, rice noodles and almonds tossed in our oriental vinaigrette.
Crisp romaine tossed in garlic Caesar dressing topped with grilled chicken, croutons and shaved parmesan.

A fresh, new blend of sweet and savory with mixed greens, cucumber, bruschetta tomatoes, edamame and red onions topped with sautéed shrimp. Served with a lemon wedge and light lemon olive oil vinaigrette on the side.
Grilled USDA select top sirloin or grilled chicken topped with chimichurri. Served with mixed greens, black bean corn salsa, a blend of cheddar cheeses, tortilla strips and house-made cilantro ranch.
A hearty salad with crispy or grilled chicken tenders on a bed of fresh greens topped with a blend of cheddar cheeses, tomatoes and a hard-boiled egg. Served with honey Dijon mustard dressing.

100% fresh, never frozen ground beef. Savor the rich flavor in this tasty original. An all-beef patty topped with two slices of pepper jack cheese, crispy onions, two strips of applewood-smoked bacon and fireball whisky-infused steak sauce. Served on a brioche bun with lettuce, tomato, onion and pickles. Served with classic fries. Cooked to a minimum of 158 degree Fahrenheit with your choice of pink or no-pink.

100% fresh, never frozen ground beef. A wake up call for your taste buds. Our juicy all-beef patty is topped with crispy hash browns, two strips of applewood smoked bacon, two slices of American cheese, ketchup and a fried egg. Served on a brioche bun with lettuce, tomato, onion and pickles. Served with classic fries. Cooked to a minimum of 158 degree Fahrenheit with your choice of pink or no-pink.

100% fresh, never frozen ground beef. All-beef patty topped with two slices of cheddar, tangy BBQ bacon ranch and three strips of applewood-smoked bacon. Served on a brioche bun with lettuce, tomato, onion and pickles. Served with classic fries. Cooked to a minimum of 158 degree Fahrenheit with your choice of pink or no-pink.

100% fresh, never frozen ground beef. Go old school with our handcrafted all-beef patty topped with your choice of two cheese slices and two strips of applewood-smoked bacon. Served with lettuce, tomato, onion and pickles on a brioche bun. Served with classic fries. Cooked to a minimum of 158 degree Fahrenheit with your choice of pink or no-pink.

Part burger, part quesadilla, all taste. This original burger creation comes piled high with 2 slices of pepper jack cheese, our signature Mexi-ranch sauce, crispy applewood-smoked bacon, fresh pico and shredded lettuce in a crisp, warm cheddar quesadilla.

Our grilled chicken breast is topped with two strips of applewood-smoked bacon and cheddar, then finished with tangy BBQ bacon ranch, crisp lettuce, tomato, onion and pickles on a brioche bun. Served with classic fries.
Sliced ham and turkey, cheddar, Swiss, two strips of applewood-smoked bacon, lettuce, tomato, mayo and honey BBQ sauce on toasted potato bread. Served with classic fries.

This crispy chicken breast creation is really kickin' with fresh iceberg lettuce, juicy tomatoes, red onion and pickles topped with the zip of classic buffalo wing sauce and cool ranch dressing. Served on a brioche bun. Served with classic fries.

Bursting with big Texas flavor, flour tortillas are filled with shredded beef brisket, spicy Texas BBQ sauce, a blend of cheddar cheeses and pico de gallo. Topped with crispy onions, a drizzle of our Mexi-ranch dressing and cilantro. Served with our signature coleslaw. Served with classic fries.
Juicy chipotle chicken with crisp lettuce, a blend of cheddar cheeses and house-made pico wrapped in a tortilla with our Mexi-ranch dipping sauce. Served with classic fries.
Ground beef burger served on a toasted bun with American cheese, lettuce, tomato and pickles.
